{"surah":{"number":76,"name":"الانسان","englishName":"Al-Insan","englishTranslation":"The Man","ayahCount":31},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:36.188Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"Has there [not] come upon man a period of time when he was not a thing [even] mentioned?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَلْ","english":"Has","translit":"hal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَتَىٰ","english":"(there) come","translit":"atā","root":"أتي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"upon","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنِ","english":"man","translit":"l-insāni","root":"أنس"},{"position":5,"arabic":"حِينٌۭ","english":"a period","translit":"ḥīnun","root":"حين"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلدَّهْرِ","english":"time","translit":"l-dahri","root":"دهر"},{"position":8,"arabic":"لَمْ","english":"not","translit":"lam","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"يَكُن","english":"he was","translit":"yakun","root":"كون"},{"position":10,"arabic":"شَيْـًۭٔا","english":"a thing","translit":"shayan","root":"شيأ"},{"position":11,"arabic":"مَّذْكُورًا","english":"mentioned","translit":"madhkūran","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"Indeed, We created man from a sperm-drop mixture that We may try him; and We made him hearing and seeing.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَا","english":"[We] created","translit":"khalaqnā","root":"خلق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ","english":"man","translit":"l-insāna","root":"أنس"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"نُّطْفَةٍ","english":"a semen-drop","translit":"nuṭ'fatin","root":"نطف"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَمْشَاجٍۢ","english":"a mixture","translit":"amshājin","root":"مشج"},{"position":7,"arabic":"نَّبْتَلِيهِ","english":"(that) We test him","translit":"nabtalīhi","root":"بلو"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَجَعَلْنَـٰهُ","english":"so We made (for) him","translit":"fajaʿalnāhu","root":"جعل"},{"position":9,"arabic":"سَمِيعًۢا","english":"hearing","translit":"samīʿan","root":"سمع"},{"position":10,"arabic":"بَصِيرًا","english":"and sight","translit":"baṣīran","root":"بصر"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"Indeed, We guided him to the way, be he grateful or be he ungrateful.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هَدَيْنَـٰهُ","english":"guided him","translit":"hadaynāhu","root":"هدي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّبِيلَ","english":"(to) the way","translit":"l-sabīla","root":"سبل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِمَّا","english":"whether","translit":"immā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"شَاكِرًۭا","english":"(he) be grateful","translit":"shākiran","root":"شكر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَإِمَّا","english":"and whether","translit":"wa-immā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَفُورًا","english":"(he) be ungrateful","translit":"kafūran","root":"كفر"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"Indeed, We have prepared for the disbelievers chains and shackles and a blaze.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَعْتَدْنَا","english":"[We] have prepared","translit":"aʿtadnā","root":"عتد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","english":"for the disbelievers","translit":"lil'kāfirīna","root":"كفر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَلَـٰسِلَا۟","english":"chains","translit":"salāsilā","root":"سلسل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَغْلَـٰلًۭا","english":"and shackles","translit":"wa-aghlālan","root":"غلل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَسَعِيرًا","english":"and a Blazing Fire","translit":"wasaʿīran","root":"سعر"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"Indeed, the righteous will drink from a cup [of wine] whose mixture is of Kafur,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْأَبْرَارَ","english":"the righteous","translit":"l-abrāra","root":"برر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَشْرَبُونَ","english":"will drink","translit":"yashrabūna","root":"شرب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَأْسٍۢ","english":"a cup","translit":"kasin","root":"كأس"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مِزَاجُهَا","english":"its mixture","translit":"mizājuhā","root":"مزج"},{"position":8,"arabic":"كَافُورًا","english":"(of) Kafur","translit":"kāfūran","root":"كفر"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"A spring of which the [righteous] servants of Allah will drink; they will make it gush forth in force [and abundance].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَيْنًۭا","english":"A spring","translit":"ʿaynan","root":"عين"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَشْرَبُ","english":"will drink","translit":"yashrabu","root":"شرب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِهَا","english":"from it","translit":"bihā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"عِبَادُ","english":"(the) slaves","translit":"ʿibādu","root":"عبد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يُفَجِّرُونَهَا","english":"causing it to gush forth","translit":"yufajjirūnahā","root":"فجر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"تَفْجِيرًۭا","english":"abundantly","translit":"tafjīran","root":"فجر"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"They [are those who] fulfill [their] vows and fear a Day whose evil will be widespread.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يُوفُونَ","english":"They fulfill","translit":"yūfūna","root":"وفي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱلنَّذْرِ","english":"the vows","translit":"bil-nadhri","root":"نذر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَيَخَافُونَ","english":"and fear","translit":"wayakhāfūna","root":"خوف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَوْمًۭا","english":"a Day","translit":"yawman","root":"يوم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"(which) is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":6,"arabic":"شَرُّهُۥ","english":"its evil","translit":"sharruhu","root":"شرر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُسْتَطِيرًۭا","english":"widespread","translit":"mus'taṭīran","root":"طير"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"And they give food in spite of love for it to the needy, the orphan, and the captive,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيُطْعِمُونَ","english":"And they feed","translit":"wayuṭ'ʿimūna","root":"طعم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلطَّعَامَ","english":"the food","translit":"l-ṭaʿāma","root":"طعم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"in spite of","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"حُبِّهِۦ","english":"love (for) it","translit":"ḥubbihi","root":"حبب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِسْكِينًۭا","english":"(to the) needy","translit":"mis'kīnan","root":"سكن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَيَتِيمًۭا","english":"and (the) orphan","translit":"wayatīman","root":"يتم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَأَسِيرًا","english":"and (the) captive","translit":"wa-asīran","root":"أسر"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"[Saying], \"We feed you only for the countenance of Allah. We wish not from you reward or gratitude.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","english":"Only","translit":"innamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نُطْعِمُكُمْ","english":"we feed you","translit":"nuṭ'ʿimukum","root":"طعم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِوَجْهِ","english":"for (the) Countenance","translit":"liwajhi","root":"وجه"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"نُرِيدُ","english":"we desire","translit":"nurīdu","root":"رود"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مِنكُمْ","english":"from you","translit":"minkum","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"جَزَآءًۭ","english":"any reward","translit":"jazāan","root":"جزي"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"شُكُورًا","english":"thanks","translit":"shukūran","root":"شكر"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"Indeed, We fear from our Lord a Day austere and distressful.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, we","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَخَافُ","english":"fear","translit":"nakhāfu","root":"خوف"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَّبِّنَا","english":"our Lord","translit":"rabbinā","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَوْمًا","english":"a Day","translit":"yawman","root":"يوم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَبُوسًۭا","english":"harsh","translit":"ʿabūsan","root":"عبس"},{"position":7,"arabic":"قَمْطَرِيرًۭا","english":"and distressful","translit":"qamṭarīran","root":"قمطر"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"So Allah will protect them from the evil of that Day and give them radiance and happiness","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَوَقَىٰهُمُ","english":"But will protect them","translit":"fawaqāhumu","root":"وقي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"شَرَّ","english":"(from the) evil","translit":"sharra","root":"شرر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"(of) that","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمِ","english":"Day","translit":"l-yawmi","root":"يوم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَلَقَّىٰهُمْ","english":"and will cause them to meet","translit":"walaqqāhum","root":"لقي"},{"position":7,"arabic":"نَضْرَةًۭ","english":"radiance","translit":"naḍratan","root":"نضر"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَسُرُورًۭا","english":"and happiness","translit":"wasurūran","root":"سرر"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And will reward them for what they patiently endured [with] a garden [in Paradise] and silk [garments].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَزَىٰهُم","english":"And will reward them","translit":"wajazāhum","root":"جزي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"because","translit":"bimā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"صَبَرُوا۟","english":"they were patient","translit":"ṣabarū","root":"صبر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَنَّةًۭ","english":"(with) a Garden","translit":"jannatan","root":"جنن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَحَرِيرًۭا","english":"and silk","translit":"waḥarīran","root":"حرر"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"[They will be] reclining therein on adorned couches. They will not see therein any [burning] sun or [freezing] cold.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مُّتَّكِـِٔينَ","english":"Reclining","translit":"muttakiīna","root":"وكأ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرَآئِكِ ۖ","english":"couches","translit":"l-arāiki","root":"أرك"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_013_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَرَوْنَ","english":"they will see","translit":"yarawna","root":"رأي","audio":"wbw/076_013_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_013_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"شَمْسًۭا","english":"sun","translit":"shamsan","root":"شمس","audio":"wbw/076_013_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_013_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"زَمْهَرِيرًۭا","english":"freezing cold","translit":"zamharīran","root":"زمهر","audio":"wbw/076_013_011.mp3"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And near above them are its shades, and its [fruit] to be picked will be lowered in compliance.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَدَانِيَةً","english":"And near","translit":"wadāniyatan","root":"دنو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"above them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ظِلَـٰلُهَا","english":"(are) its shades","translit":"ẓilāluhā","root":"ظلل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَذُلِّلَتْ","english":"and will hang low","translit":"wadhullilat","root":"ذلل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"قُطُوفُهَا","english":"its cluster of fruits","translit":"quṭūfuhā","root":"قطف"},{"position":6,"arabic":"تَذْلِيلًۭا","english":"dangling low","translit":"tadhlīlan","root":"ذلل"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"And there will be circulated among them vessels of silver and cups having been [created] clear [as glass],","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيُطَافُ","english":"And will be circulated","translit":"wayuṭāfu","root":"طوف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِم","english":"among them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِـَٔانِيَةٍۢ","english":"vessels","translit":"biāniyatin","root":"أني"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"فِضَّةٍۢ","english":"silver","translit":"fiḍḍatin","root":"فضض"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَكْوَابٍۢ","english":"and cups","translit":"wa-akwābin","root":"كوب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَانَتْ","english":"(that) are","translit":"kānat","root":"كون"},{"position":8,"arabic":"قَوَارِيرَا۠","english":"(of) crystal","translit":"qawārīrā","root":"قرر"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"Clear glasses [made] from silver of which they have determined the measure.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَوَارِيرَا۟","english":"Crystal-clear","translit":"qawārīrā","root":"قرر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِضَّةٍۢ","english":"silver","translit":"fiḍḍatin","root":"فضض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَدَّرُوهَا","english":"They will determine its","translit":"qaddarūhā","root":"قدر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَقْدِيرًۭا","english":"measure","translit":"taqdīran","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"And they will be given to drink a cup [of wine] whose mixture is of ginger","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيُسْقَوْنَ","english":"And they will be given to drink","translit":"wayus'qawna","root":"سقي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَأْسًۭا","english":"a cup","translit":"kasan","root":"كأس"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِزَاجُهَا","english":"its mixture","translit":"mizājuhā","root":"مزج"},{"position":6,"arabic":"زَنجَبِيلًا","english":"(of) Zanjabil","translit":"zanjabīlan","root":""}]},{"number":18,"translation":"[From] a fountain within Paradise named Salsabeel.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَيْنًۭا","english":"A spring","translit":"ʿaynan","root":"عين"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تُسَمَّىٰ","english":"named","translit":"tusammā","root":"سمو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَلْسَبِيلًۭا","english":"Salsabil","translit":"salsabīlan","root":""}]},{"number":19,"translation":"There will circulate among them young boys made eternal. When you see them, you would think them [as beautiful as] scattered pearls.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَيَطُوفُ","english":"And will circulate","translit":"wayaṭūfu","root":"طوف","audio":"wbw/076_019_002.mp3"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"among them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_019_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وِلْدَٰنٌۭ","english":"young boys","translit":"wil'dānun","root":"ولد","audio":"wbw/076_019_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُّخَلَّدُونَ","english":"made eternal","translit":"mukhalladūna","root":"خلد","audio":"wbw/076_019_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"When","translit":"idhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_019_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"رَأَيْتَهُمْ","english":"you see them","translit":"ra-aytahum","root":"رأي","audio":"wbw/076_019_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"حَسِبْتَهُمْ","english":"you would think them","translit":"ḥasib'tahum","root":"حسب","audio":"wbw/076_019_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"لُؤْلُؤًۭا","english":"(to be) pearls","translit":"lu'lu-an","root":"لؤلؤ","audio":"wbw/076_019_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مَّنثُورًۭا","english":"scattered","translit":"manthūran","root":"نثر","audio":"wbw/076_019_010.mp3"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"And when you look there [in Paradise], you will see pleasure and great dominion.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَأَيْتَ","english":"you look","translit":"ra-ayta","root":"رأي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ثَمَّ","english":"then","translit":"thamma","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَأَيْتَ","english":"you will see","translit":"ra-ayta","root":"رأي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَعِيمًۭا","english":"blessings","translit":"naʿīman","root":"نعم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمُلْكًۭا","english":"and a kingdom","translit":"wamul'kan","root":"ملك"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَبِيرًا","english":"great","translit":"kabīran","root":"كبر"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"Upon the inhabitants will be green garments of fine silk and brocade. And they will be adorned with bracelets of silver, and their Lord will give them a purifying drink.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَـٰلِيَهُمْ","english":"Upon them","translit":"ʿāliyahum","root":"علو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ثِيَابُ","english":"(will be) garments","translit":"thiyābu","root":"ثوب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"سُندُسٍ","english":"(of) fine silk","translit":"sundusin","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"خُضْرٌۭ","english":"green","translit":"khuḍ'run","root":"خضر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِسْتَبْرَقٌۭ ۖ","english":"and heavy brocade","translit":"wa-is'tabraqun","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَحُلُّوٓا۟","english":"And they will be adorned","translit":"waḥullū","root":"حلي","audio":"wbw/076_021_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَسَاوِرَ","english":"(with) bracelets","translit":"asāwira","root":"سور","audio":"wbw/076_021_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_021_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فِضَّةٍۢ","english":"silver","translit":"fiḍḍatin","root":"فضض","audio":"wbw/076_021_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَسَقَىٰهُمْ","english":"and will give them to drink","translit":"wasaqāhum","root":"سقي","audio":"wbw/076_021_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"رَبُّهُمْ","english":"their Lord","translit":"rabbuhum","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/076_021_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"شَرَابًۭا","english":"a drink","translit":"sharāban","root":"شرب","audio":"wbw/076_021_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"طَهُورًا","english":"pure","translit":"ṭahūran","root":"طهر","audio":"wbw/076_021_014.mp3"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"[And it will be said], \"Indeed, this is for you a reward, and your effort has been appreciated.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"this","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"جَزَآءًۭ","english":"a reward","translit":"jazāan","root":"جزي"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَكَانَ","english":"and has been","translit":"wakāna","root":"كون"},{"position":7,"arabic":"سَعْيُكُم","english":"your effort","translit":"saʿyukum","root":"سعي"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مَّشْكُورًا","english":"appreciated","translit":"mashkūran","root":"شكر"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"Indeed, it is We who have sent down to you, [O Muhammad], the Qur'an progressively.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","english":"[We]","translit":"naḥnu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَزَّلْنَا","english":"[We] revealed","translit":"nazzalnā","root":"نزل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَيْكَ","english":"to you","translit":"ʿalayka","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانَ","english":"the Quran","translit":"l-qur'āna","root":"قرأ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"تَنزِيلًۭا","english":"progressively","translit":"tanzīlan","root":"نزل"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"So be patient for the decision of your Lord and do not obey from among them a sinner or ungrateful [disbeliever].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱصْبِرْ","english":"So be patient","translit":"fa-iṣ'bir","root":"صبر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِحُكْمِ","english":"for (the) Command","translit":"liḥuk'mi","root":"حكم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and (do) not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تُطِعْ","english":"obey","translit":"tuṭiʿ","root":"طوع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِنْهُمْ","english":"from them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ءَاثِمًا","english":"any sinner","translit":"āthiman","root":"أثم"},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَوْ","english":"or","translit":"aw","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"كَفُورًۭا","english":"disbeliever","translit":"kafūran","root":"كفر"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"And mention the name of your Lord [in prayer] morning and evening","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱذْكُرِ","english":"And remember","translit":"wa-udh'kuri","root":"ذكر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱسْمَ","english":"(the) name","translit":"is'ma","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بُكْرَةًۭ","english":"morning","translit":"buk'ratan","root":"بكر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَصِيلًۭا","english":"and evening","translit":"wa-aṣīlan","root":"أصل"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"And during the night prostrate to Him and exalt Him a long [part of the] night.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمِنَ","english":"And of","translit":"wamina","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّيْلِ","english":"the night","translit":"al-layli","root":"ليل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَٱسْجُدْ","english":"prostrate","translit":"fa-us'jud","root":"سجد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","english":"to Him","translit":"lahu","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَسَبِّحْهُ","english":"and glorify Him","translit":"wasabbiḥ'hu","root":"سبح"},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَيْلًۭا","english":"a night","translit":"laylan","root":"ليل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"طَوِيلًا","english":"long","translit":"ṭawīlan","root":"طول"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"Indeed, these [disbelievers] love the immediate and leave behind them a grave Day.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ","english":"these","translit":"hāulāi","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يُحِبُّونَ","english":"love","translit":"yuḥibbūna","root":"حبب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْعَاجِلَةَ","english":"the immediate","translit":"l-ʿājilata","root":"عجل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَيَذَرُونَ","english":"and leave","translit":"wayadharūna","root":"وذر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَرَآءَهُمْ","english":"behind them","translit":"warāahum","root":"وري"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَوْمًۭا","english":"a Day","translit":"yawman","root":"يوم"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ثَقِيلًۭا","english":"grave","translit":"thaqīlan","root":"ثقل"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"We have created them and strengthened their forms, and when We will, We can change their likenesses with [complete] alteration.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"نَّحْنُ","english":"We","translit":"naḥnu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَـٰهُمْ","english":"created them","translit":"khalaqnāhum","root":"خلق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَشَدَدْنَآ","english":"and We strengthened","translit":"washadadnā","root":"شدد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَسْرَهُمْ ۖ","english":"their forms","translit":"asrahum","root":"أسر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"and when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_028_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"شِئْنَا","english":"We will","translit":"shi'nā","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/076_028_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"بَدَّلْنَآ","english":"We can change","translit":"baddalnā","root":"بدل","audio":"wbw/076_028_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَمْثَـٰلَهُمْ","english":"their likeness[es]","translit":"amthālahum","root":"مثل","audio":"wbw/076_028_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"تَبْدِيلًا","english":"(with) a change","translit":"tabdīlan","root":"بدل","audio":"wbw/076_028_010.mp3"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"Indeed, this is a reminder, so he who wills may take to his Lord a way.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هَـٰذِهِۦ","english":"this","translit":"hādhihi","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَذْكِرَةٌۭ ۖ","english":"(is) a reminder","translit":"tadhkiratun","root":"ذكر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَمَن","english":"so whoever","translit":"faman","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_029_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"شَآءَ","english":"wills","translit":"shāa","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/076_029_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱتَّخَذَ","english":"let him take","translit":"ittakhadha","root":"أخذ","audio":"wbw/076_029_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_029_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"رَبِّهِۦ","english":"his Lord","translit":"rabbihi","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/076_029_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"سَبِيلًۭا","english":"a way","translit":"sabīlan","root":"سبل","audio":"wbw/076_029_010.mp3"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"And you do not will except that Allah wills. Indeed, Allah is ever Knowing and Wise.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَشَآءُونَ","english":"you will","translit":"tashāūna","root":"شيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَشَآءَ","english":"wills","translit":"yashāa","root":"شيأ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۚ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_030_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/076_030_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/076_030_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"عَلِيمًا","english":"All-Knower","translit":"ʿalīman","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/076_030_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"حَكِيمًۭا","english":"All-Wise","translit":"ḥakīman","root":"حكم","audio":"wbw/076_030_012.mp3"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"He admits whom He wills into His mercy; but the wrongdoers - He has prepared for them a painful punishment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يُدْخِلُ","english":"He admits","translit":"yud'khilu","root":"دخل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَن","english":"whom","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَشَآءُ","english":"He wills","translit":"yashāu","root":"شيأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","english":"into","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَحْمَتِهِۦ ۚ","english":"His mercy","translit":"raḥmatihi","root":"رحم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ","english":"but (for) the wrongdoers","translit":"wal-ẓālimīna","root":"ظلم","audio":"wbw/076_031_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَعَدَّ","english":"He has prepared","translit":"aʿadda","root":"عدد","audio":"wbw/076_031_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"for them","translit":"lahum","root":"","audio":"wbw/076_031_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"عَذَابًا","english":"a punishment","translit":"ʿadhāban","root":"عذب","audio":"wbw/076_031_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"أَلِيمًۢا","english":"painful","translit":"alīman","root":"ألم","audio":"wbw/076_031_011.mp3"}]}]}
